{"tid":2333452,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中芯國際稱美國制裁對10納米先進工藝研發有重大不利","createTime":"2020-12-20T12:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T17:03:35.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f9356b78ba4125d0caf2e495eed756da83607a0b","tid":2333452,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T12:03:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566291-20201220.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566291-20201220.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIUcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=af13484f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566291-20201220.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9353725b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566291-20201220.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國商務部日前公布，將中國最大晶片製造商中芯國際列入貿易黑名單。<br />\n<br />\n中芯國際表示，關注美國商務部以保護美國國家安全和外交利益為由，將公司及其部分子公司及參股公司列入「實體清單」，經公司初步評估，事件對公司短期營運及財務狀況，無重大不利影響，但對10納米及以下先進工藝的研發及產能建設，有重大不利影響，公司將持續與美國政府相關部門溝通，並視情況採取一切可行措施，積極尋求解決方案，力爭將不利影響降到最低。<br />\n<br />\n中芯國際表示，公司將根據後續發展情況，嚴格遵守相關規則，及時履行資訊披露義務，呼籲投資者及時關注公司公告，注意投資風險。"},{"pid":"03a5f62f5e0c1a03a620cb0fbcebf91ed7854dec","tid":2333452,"uid":155095,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T12:05:43.000Z","msg":"學華為自煮燃發囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg6-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/120275205_379797103411161_5155719634057329148_n.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=pDJupvK8Rw8AX-KHNlZ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg6-1.fna&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=51a7cad60065712b0d653222a5c8b1c9&amp;oe=6004E2D3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg6-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F120275205_379797103411161_5155719634057329148_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110